Inspect is an action extension ( works in both Safari and Chrome) that allows you to inspect and export websites' https certificate information. You can as well as copy or input https url manually in the main app to inspect it.

Features:

* View SSL certificates chain
* View X509 certificate information
* Export selected certificate
* WOT rating integrations
* Shortcut to scan in SSLLabs.com
* Recently lookup histories
* Possible MITM detections

If you have any questions please do not hesitate to contact support@fourplex.in

Stichting Reformatorische Omroep (RO) heeft als doelstelling om radio- en videoprogramma's voor gezinnen in de hele gereformeerde gezindte te maken en zendt uit via het internet. Daardoor zijn de programma's met een computer te beluisteren en te bekijken in Nederland en in het buitenland. Verder zijn de programma's zonder computer te ontvangen met een internetradio, via de kerktelefoon (Kerkomroep) en in veel bejaarden- en verpleegtehuizen.

Personal tour guides in every city of the world.
PRIVATE GUIDE Service helps guides and tourists find each other in any part of the world. You can find your personal tour guide in any city with just a few clicks!
The tourists can find all of the available guides in a particular city or country, get guides’ descriptions and contact them directly after easily signing up within the application. You can search for the guide by their geographical location; find the guide closest to you! Contact the guide to discuss all of the details of your tour and then meet with them for a guided tour! The communication between tour guide and tourist is not limited. We offer a fully functional instant messenger.
Tour guides and private tour escorts, you can sign up in our application and present your services. Publish your descriptions, skills, and tours!
After signing up, the tour guides have a convenient platform for presenting and promoting their services all around the world for all of the tourists to see. This data will be available for all search engines. You can also control your inquiry history and communications with tourists.

The official app for USENIX Events!

App Features: 

*Full Schedule*
Browse the entire schedule for USENIX events. You can filter by color-coded types, venues or search for what you need. Get the full details of every event without having to crack open an event guide.

*My Schedule*
If you have already created a schedule online, you can login to view it on your phone and make on-the-go changes. If you are new, create an account and instantly save your favorites.

*Social Friend Finder*
Don't miss out on the good stuff. Connect your Facebook account and view the event schedule based on what you're friends will be attending.

*Offline Caching*
Fully equipped with offline storage to make sure you always have your schedule, even if your connection drops.

Visit https://www.usenix.org/conferences for additional event information.
